{"tid":1046025,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"筲箕灣地盤塌棚架工人墮地 警封東區走廊西行慢線","createTime":"2019-03-04T02:38:29.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T03:17:15.000Z","uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"e1d14b481081ae7aeb3db69ce9f4fa585b9e4e5a","tid":1046025,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:38:29.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190304/59327314\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F59327314&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4PxvqPrKL%2FWP0%2BN3ppmbOOw%3D&h=ce627f99\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F59327314&h=de5fc5b5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190304/59327314</a><br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣地盤塌棚架工人墮地 警封東區走廊西行慢線<br />\n<br />\n筲箕灣阿公岩村道5號一個翻新地盤，早上9時14分，工人在一個離地5米高的棚架工作期間，棚架突然倒塌，一名工人亦連棚架一同倒下墮地，工人受傷仍然清醒，獲送院治理，整幅棚架倒塌挨到東區走廊橋邊，警方正在東區走廊實施交通管制，封西行慢線善後。<br />\n<br />\n肇事地盤當時有433名工人開工，為防棚架有進一步倒塌危機，大批工人被疏散到空曠位置。<br />\n<br />\n讀者劉先生剛行經上址地盤，赫見地盤棚架塌下，整幅挨到對面行車天橋，一名工人亦從約二樓的高度，連同棚架倒下墮地，工人受傷清醒，被工友扶到一旁等候救援。<br />\n<br />\n廣告"},{"pid":"06fcba243e0b4adb0f6dd4278beccda7f50953f8","tid":1046025,"uid":152476,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:39:01.000Z","msg":"地盤又出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8a86996d56b825e05fc00de0804a9eac30b9283","tid":1046025,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"搭棚不知幾穩陣<br />\n十號波都唔怕塌<br />\n外國個啲鋼架好流架一打風就要拆"},{"pid":"880eba8c51b4434548e86e8656f75d1e54275a6f","tid":1046025,"uid":163502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c8a86996d56b825e05fc00de0804a9eac30b9283","tid":1046025,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T02:40:20.000Z","msg":"搭棚不知幾穩陣